parameters.text:
=Create 3 high-converting static ad concepts with the following specifications:
BRAND DETAILS:

Business: {{$json['Business Name'] || 'Specify business name'}}
Service/Product: {{$json['Service Description'] || 'Describe offering'}}
Industry/Category: {{$json['Industry'] || 'Specify industry'}}
Unique Value Proposition: {{$json['UVP'] || 'What makes this unique?'}}

Website:
{{ $json.Website }}

TARGET AUDIENCE:

Primary Demographic: {{$json['Target Audience'] || 'Define target audience'}}
Pain Points: {{$json['Pain Points'] || 'List main challenges/problems'}}
Desired Outcomes: {{$json['Desired Outcomes'] || 'What do they want to achieve?'}}
Platform Behavior: {{$json['Platform Preference'] || 'Where do they spend time online?'}}

BRAND GUIDELINES:

Visual Style: {{$json['Brand Style'] || 'modern|classic|playful|luxury|minimal'}}
Primary Colors: {{$json['Primary Brand Colors'] || '#HEX codes preferred'}}
Secondary Colors: {{$json['Secondary Colors'] || 'Accent colors if any'}}
Brand Voice: {{$json['Brand Voice'] || 'professional|friendly|bold|innovative'}}
Existing Assets: {{$json['Assets Available'] || 'logos|photos|illustrations'}}

CAMPAIGN OBJECTIVES:

Primary Goal: {{$json['Campaign Goal'] || 'conversions|leads|awareness|traffic'}}
Key Benefits: {{$json['Key Benefits'] || 'List top 3 benefits'}}
Social Proof: {{$json['Social Proof'] || 'testimonials|stats|awards|clients'}}
Urgency/Offer: {{$json['Special Offer'] || 'Any time-sensitive elements?'}}

TECHNICAL REQUIREMENTS:

Primary Platform: {{$json['Primary Platform'] || 'Facebook|Instagram|LinkedIn|Google'}}
Ad Dimensions: {{$json['Dimensions'] || 'Auto-select based on platform'}}
Text Limitations: {{$json['Text Limits'] || 'Platform default'}}
Compliance Needs: {{$json['Compliance'] || 'Any disclaimers needed?'}}

COMPETITIVE CONTEXT:

Main Competitors: {{$json['Competitors'] || 'List top 3'}}
Differentiation: {{$json['Differentiation'] || 'How to stand out?'}}
Market Position: {{$json['Market Position'] || 'leader|challenger|disruptor|niche'}}

DELIVERABLES:
Generate 3 distinct concepts using these psychological frameworks:

Problem-Agitation-Solution (PAS) - Focus on pain point resolution
Aspiration-Bridge-Achievement (ABA) - Emphasize transformation
Authority-Evidence-Trust (AET) - Highlight credibility and proof

For each concept, provide:

Complete image generation prompt with specific style, composition, and elements
All copy elements (headline, body, CTA)
Design strategy and visual hierarchy
Psychological triggers employed
Platform-specific optimization notes

Return response in structured JSON format as specified in system instructions.

RESEARCH DIRECTIVE:
If needed, search for:

Current industry advertising trends
Competitor ad strategies
Platform-specific best practices for {{$json['Industry'] || 'this industry'}}
Recent performance benchmarks for similar campaigns

